[vc_row][vc_column][vc_gallery interval=”5″ images=”5289,5290,5291″ img_size=”large”][vc_column_text]Driving school is an entity that teaches the skills (training) to the candidates for drivers of the vehicles.

Candidate for driver is a person who is enrolled in driving school for training for driver.

Driving license is a public document which is issued by the competent authority and which proves the right to operate certain categories of vehicles;

[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]
